        crm:P3_has_note          "Modular microservices (ARTEMIS WP9 Task 9.2) for probabilistic modelling, EOV (Environmental and Operational Variations) correlation, and synthetic data generation. Enables extrapolation of structural and environmental evolutions from historical IoT datasets and experimental monitoring campaigns. Supports correlation analysis between vibration response and environmental conditions for heritage structural assessment." ;
